ese events will show up on the Calendar tab of a group home page.</li><li>Group RSS feed. If there is interesting content coming from outside this site that you want your group to track, pull that content in as an RSS feed to the site.</li></ul><p>There&#39;s more to building a community than the technology; it&#39;s the people &amp; participation that makes a community work. This set of content types should give you all the choices you need to jump-start this community.</p>\";s:6:\"teaser\";s:136:\"<p>In Drupal Commons, all content is all created within the context of a &quot;Group&quot;. Start exploring how to use your site by:</p>\";s:22:\"field_featured_content\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:5:\"value\";s:8:\"Featured\";}}s:8:\"taxonomy\";a:1:{s:4:\"tags\";a:1:{i:2;s:49:\"content types, getting started, groups, jumpstart\";}}s:9:\"og_public\";i:1;s:9:\"og_groups\";a:1:{i:1;s:1:\"1\";}s:18:\"field_group_sticky\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:5:\"value\";N;}}s:20:\"field_content_images\";a:1:{i:0;N;}s:8:\"og_theme\";N;s:6:\"is_new\";b:1;s:3:\"log\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"changed\";i:1313585261;s:9:\"timestamp\";i:1313585261;s:3:\"vid\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"language\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"moderate\";i:0;s:4:\"tnid\";i:0;s:9:\"translate\";i:0;s:3:\"nid\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"path\";s:37:\"discussion/jumpstarting-our-community\";}s:5:\"_info\";a:5:{s:5:\"label\";s:7:\"content\";s:5:\"class\";s:20:\"rules_data_type_node\";s:7:\"savable\";b:1;s:12:\"identifiable\";b:1;s:6:\"module\";s:4:\"Node\";}s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"node\";}s:6:\"_state\";a:2:{s:8:\"set_info\";a:3:{s:5:\"label\";s:24:\"After saving new content\";s:6:\"module\";s:4:\"Node\";s:9:\"arguments\";a:3:{s:4:\"node\";a:2:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"node\";s:5:\"label\";s:15:\"created content\";}s:6:\"author\";a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"user\";s:5:\"label\";s:16:\"content\'s author\";s:7:\"handler\";s:33:\"rules_events_argument_node_author\";}s:4:\"user\";a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"user\";s:5:\"label\";s:11:\"acting user\";s:7:\"handler\";s:33:\"rules_events_argument_global_us